[[SECTION]]
UID: EL-158
TITLE: Performance Requirements

[WORK_ITEM]
UID: EL-159_532dae219592ec939c858df6868d53b6
POLARION_ID: EL-159
STATUS: Reviewed
TITLE: System should meet the following acceptance criteria
DESCRIPTION: >>>

.. list-table::
    :widths: 1 1
    :header-rows: 1

    * - Use Case
      - Acceptable Response Time
    * - Open Application Portal
      - 2 sec
    * - Render Search Result
      - 1 sec
    * - Open Book Detail
      - 0.5 sec
    * - Open Author Detail
      - 0.5 sec

<<<
COMMENT: >>>
Item was e-signed

Approval verdict:
Approved

<<<

