[[SECTION]]
UID: EL-155
TITLE: Browser Compatibility

[WORK_ITEM]
UID: EL-160_532dae219592ec939c858df6868d53b6
POLARION_ID: EL-160
STATUS: Reviewed
TITLE: System must support all following web browsers
DESCRIPTION: >>>

.. list-table::
    :widths: 1 1
    :header-rows: 1

    * - Browser
      - Support Level
    * - IE 10
      - Full Support
    * - IE 9
      - Full Support
    * - IE 8
      - Layout issues are acceptable
    * - Firefox 24+
      - Full Support
    * - Chrome 32+
      - Full Support

<<<

